cs.NE, cs.ET, cs.EM, cs.CE, cs.LG 

The paper describes a current to frequency converter for real-time monitoring of analog currents in neuromorphic electronic systems. The focus is on the design and implementation of the circuit, which is relevant to the fields of neural engineering (cs.NE), electronic engineering (cs.ET), and circuit design (cs.CE). The paper also discusses the experimental results obtained from interfacing the circuit with silicon neuron and synapse circuits, which is relevant to the field of electromagnetics (cs.EM) and machine learning (cs.LG).
